0.09

    - Switch to Module::Build
    - first() and last() should construct new object, but not modify self
      (Oleg++)

0.08

    - added ->map and ->filter methods
      (Hiroki Honda)
    - fixed as (empty)->first->size and (empty)->last->size return 0
      (Hiroki Honda)

